description: Luzern hold first-leg advantage over Djurgarden
title: Luzern hold first-leg advantage over Djurgarden
title_page: Luzern hold first-leg advantage over Djurgarden - BBC Sport
maintext:
Hibernian will need to overcome a 2-1 defeat to progress in Europa Conference League qualifying, as will potential next round opponents Djurgarden.
The Swedish side fell to a first-leg loss at home to Switzerland's Luzern, with the winners set to play either Hibs or Inter Club D'Escaldes in a third-round qualifier.
The second legs of both ties take place next Thursday.
